---
title: Mediterranean Skillet Chicken with Bulgur, Zucchini and Apricots
description: Bulgur is a kind of dried cracked wheat common in Middle Eastern cuisine. In this recipe, we cook it with sweet apricots, colourful veggies, and a dusting of bright lemon zest for a deliciously citrusy aroma.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-skillet-chicken-65629cd0.jpg
